msgid ""
"Hotfix release for UI initialization issues and notification improvements."
msgstr ""

#: ../data/com.github.d3msudo.anura.metainfo.xml.in:44
msgid ""
"Fixed missing Adw.init() call causing \"greyed out UI\" on some systems."
